    <item>
      <title>随着现金储备的持续，美联储央行工具的使用增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/use-of-fed-central-bank-tool-grows-as-cash-stockpiling-continues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外国央行对美联储一项关键工具的使用量连续第三周上升，这表明世界各地的政策制定者在警告他们将采取措施支撑本国货币的同时，仍在继续建立现金头寸。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-04/use-of-fed-central-bank-tool-grows-as-cash-stockpiling-continues</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Apr 2024 21:05:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
